nhc_headline: ...JULIETTE HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...JULIETTE HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 2:00 AM PDT Thu Aug 28 the center of Juliette was located near 25.4, -120.8 with movement N at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1008 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
